screen_desc: A mobile screen displays a prompt asking the user to "Continue with" one of two phone numbers: "0888 828 927" or "0356 844 406." Below these options, there is a link labeled "NONE OF THE ABOVE." The screen also shows the time as 10:56 AM, along with various status icons for notifications, signal strength, Wi-Fi, battery level (100%), and Bluetooth. The background is black, and the prompt is in a white box. At the bottom of the screen, there are navigation buttons for recent apps, home, and back.
